snippet.title: Screaming Loaf: Android Game Trailer
snippet.description:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ashumbesher.screamingloaf

Screaming Loaf is a wacky 2D puzzle-platform game. Play as Loaf and shatter the enemy jam jars with your screams. Split into sliced bread to be in multiple places at once. Don't let the fiendish fillings make you into sandwiches!

Download it for free on Android.

#indiegame #mobilegame #androidgame #gametrailer #gaming
